ef="https://blizzardbikeclub.com/">Blizzard Bicycle Club</a></li><li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1750608511679549/?mibextid=6NoCDW">Northland Trail Blazers Snowmobile Club</a></li><li><a href="https://www.pgbrs.org/">Prince George Backcountry Recreation Society</a></li><li><a href="https://pgsc-bcsf.silkstart.com/cpages/home">Prince George Snowmobile Club</a></li><li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/swancitysnowmobileclub/">Swan City Snowmobile Club</a></li><li><a href="http://www.wnms.ca/">Wolverine Nordic &amp; Mountain Society</a></li><li><a href="https://www.scouts.ca/councils/western/cascadia/cascadia-council-news-and-events/>Scouts Canada, Cascadia Council</a>
                    
            
